{"tid":1947691,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"「月供股票入」 從日本呢個例子中睇到，疫情好快就會解決","createTime":"2020-03-28T12:41:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T00:07:55.000Z","uid":123335,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0078e7d014de31f8963b81eefc63f72cec214a0a","tid":1947691,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:41:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y3Mtt7g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY3Mtt7g.png&h=9426bfce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本初初都有份爆發<br />\n但好快就控制到疫情<br />\n目前只係得 1499 人確診 <br />\n可見，武漢肺炎冇想像中咁難控制<br />\n只要歐美肯認錯，帶返口罩，認真對待疫情<br />\n相信數字上好快會放緩<br />\n<br />\n你見美國確診人數突然大量上升<br />\n係因為加快左檢疫，務求盡快鎖定所有確診者<br />\n減少病毒進一步擴散出去<br />\n呢一點反而有效加快控制疫情<br />\n距離確診數字上放緩嘅日子不遠了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n主要有兩點好關鍵：<br />\n1）開始見到歐美疫情確診數字有放緩嘅曙光<br />\n2）無限QE (量化寬鬆) 導致現金貶值，股票 or 實物商品相對上會升值<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老實講<br />\n我就覺得而家係月供嘅好時機<br />\n你地點睇？？<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4adfe285e3770afb33fa7678e8923e4cea04752","tid":1947691,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:42:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d327db425a3618f049411ef24403d1621917efd","tid":1947691,"uid":60635,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:43:09.000Z","msg":"日本又爆緊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n輸撚死你呀"},{"pid":"892e92b91858af0feeb606415b54da3e4edc1357","tid":1947691,"uid":210280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:43:23.000Z","msg":"唔月供 而家就一炮入<br />\n淆佢老母咩"},{"pid":"d7fffd7674740f94c42d0b8cf433cbd35f3fafdc","tid":1947691,"uid":1400,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:44:08.000Z","msg":"關月供咩事？<br />\n你覺得宜家入市好，點解唔一炮過入？"},{"pid":"d52c27518d09730b5bd17ad15796d2baf79c5264","tid":1947691,"uid":298115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:44:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f04bd75a587b9193c2d21932320813bd04141ce5","tid":1947691,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d7fffd7674740f94c42d0b8cf433cbd35f3fafdc","tid":1947691,"uid":1400,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:44:08.000Z","msg":"關月供咩事？<br />\n你覺得宜家入市好，點解唔一炮過入？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:45:13.000Z","msg":"依家開始月供<br />\n「進可攻，退可守」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一炮過反而我覺得有啲唔理性"},{"pid":"cc8b9b1902c3c17894de9c2420124a4865dfcafa","tid":1947691,"uid":69872,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d7fffd7674740f94c42d0b8cf433cbd35f3fafdc","tid":1947691,"uid":1400,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:44:08.000Z","msg":"關月供咩事？<br />\n你覺得宜家入市好，點解唔一炮過入？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:45:36.000Z","msg":"如果預期到有段時間低位 可能係一年至年半時間 月供係咪一個較好選擇"},{"pid":"d8e70e57554ffd9312e6dc7ff1e4fd9fd8c70901","tid":1947691,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cc8b9b1902c3c17894de9c2420124a4865dfcafa","tid":1947691,"uid":69872,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d7fffd7674740f94c42d0b8cf433cbd35f3fafdc","tid":1947691,"uid":1400,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:44:08.000Z","msg":"關月供咩事？<br />\n你覺得宜家入市好，點解唔一炮過入？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:45:36.000Z","msg":"如果預期到有段時間低位 可能係一年至年半時間 月供係咪一個較好選擇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:46:57.000Z","msg":"I think so <br />\n月供會比較穩健"},{"pid":"5de20daea35cdc8412ba172bfcc15ffd8d9101ed","tid":1947691,"uid":100809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:48:58.000Z","msg":"控制到 唔代表可以復工wo<br />\n要控制有幾難 下令戒嚴封城宵禁 中招人數即時降低啦<br />\n但佢地照樣